    "calculator.one_rep_warning": "Never, under any circumstance should you attempt a one rep max alone. We would recommend taking two spotters (one for each side of the bar) at least. Safety should be kept in mind at all times.",
    "calculator.one_rep_method": 'This method is based on a formula from "Maximum based on reps" by J. Landers, published in 1985 in an NSCA journal.',
